{"tid":2405571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傑出公務員：初一上班初步確診","createTime":"2021-02-12T12:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T21:36:29.000Z","uid":5195,"like":179,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"28ca8a16bccef250a4dd9457003dcd20a3e69d4e","tid":2405571,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"運輸署今日（二月十二日）得悉一名技術主任初步確診2019冠狀病毒病。<br />\n<br />\n　　該名人員的辦公室地點位於九龍油麻地海庭道11號西九龍政府合署南座15樓，該樓層並非公眾樓層，並不對外開放。他最近一次上班日期為<span class=\"red\">二月十二日上午。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　該名人員最近沒有外遊紀錄，於辦公室工作時均佩戴口罩及遵守其他防疫措施。運輸署會繼續積極配合衞生防護中心的防疫措施。該名人員的工作地點亦會按照中心指引安排全面清潔和消毒，包括所有公用設施。"},{"pid":"a26db1bae0900b87d484e8b547da1326f2f2bea3","tid":2405571,"uid":178875,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5N6beUu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5N6beUu.gif&h=4c656ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n命仔事小<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得返工事大<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e248b6db8ab0cd68ca8ad6ebe45525127d6ec086","tid":2405571,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a5b0ff1b295067d1024a403f699aeebb8128be","tid":2405571,"uid":3122,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"咩事初一都要返"},{"pid":"07d68c476cb6c85e62899baf842622d7e4824474","tid":240557